{"tid":1794300,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"謝峰：絕大多數香港青年都傳承了愛國愛港優良傳統","createTime":"2019-12-23T04:20:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T07:46:18.000Z","uid":216992,"like":3,"dislike":59,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"b38aa92a44ebf29034f91617f9b47c89806781aa","tid":1794300,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T04:20:30.000Z","msg":"外交部駐港特派員謝峰出席活動致辭時表示，半年多來的修例風波，將香港推到回歸以來最危急的境地，一些青年人迷失街頭、違法施暴，讓人感到義憤和痛心。但他認為，「黑衣暴徒」只是一小撮，他們不是香港青年的代表，而絕大多數香港青年都傳承了愛國愛港優良傳統，是香港重整行裝再出發的希望。<br />\n<br />\n謝峰又提出，愛國是人類共同堅守的主流價值觀，並非抽象，而是實實在在，一個不熱愛自己國家的人，永遠不會得到別人的尊重。他說，愛國就要真心擁護一國兩制，堅決反對港獨，反對外部勢力干預，以做國家主權安全的捍衛者和一國兩制事業的接班人為榮。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1499157-20191223.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1499157-20191223.htm&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwUbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=b3f1b6c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1499157-20191223.htm&h=1f9a4e5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1499157-20191223.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c51871e7ded64f1fd91d6bb973164c4875422107","tid":1794300,"uid":272603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T04:20:52.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借個位黎<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">新德國聯署</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">德國聯邦議院《全球馬格尼茨基法案》</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">仲差44000人!!!!</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">目標50000人</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets